<div class="com-share" data-id="22276" data-title="《为什么美国人特别敢说“我爱你”？｜好奇心人类学》，来自@好奇心日报" data-pic="http://www.qdaily.com/system/articles/articleshows/22276/medium/22276.jpg?1455511775" data-url="http://www.qdaily.com/mobile/articles/22276.html" data-weiboAppkey="2462590045">
